item.title: Goldfish - Indigoo
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
I really like the part (I guess the dubstep-ish part) where you introduce the staccato melodic instruments, really cool! I can’t really tell what’s samples and what’s not, if there are any samples. That flabby bass though is not doing the track any favors it first comes in at 1:04 it’s like an engine idling… I was hoping for something with a little more definition or bite.

I like it though, the broken up elements really drew my attention
